org.sakaiproject.jsf.model

Interface PhaseAware

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddSectionsBean, AssignmentBean, AssignmentDetailsBean, ConfigBean, CourseDependentBean, CourseGradeDetailsBean, EditManagersBean, EditSectionBean, EditStudentsBean, EditStudentSectionsBean, EnrollmentTableBean, ExportResponsesBean, FeedbackOptionsBean, FilteredSectionListingBean, GradebookBean, GradebookDependentBean, GradebookSetupBean, GraderRulesBean, InitializableBean, InitializableBean, InstructorViewBean, LoginAsBean, LoginBean, NavMenuBean, OptionsBean, OverviewBean, OverviewBean, PreferencesBean, QuestionScoresBean, RemoveAssignmentBean, RosterBean, RosterBean, SelectGradebookBean, SpreadsheetRemoveBean, SpreadsheetUploadBean, StudentViewBean, StudentViewBean, SubmissionStatusBean, TotalScoresBean, ViewByStudentBean

    public interface PhaseAware
    Beans that wish to be notified of interesting transitions in the JSF request life cycle should implement this interface.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void endProcessUpdates()
      Called after the component has finished the Update Model Values phase.
      void endProcessValidators()
      Called after the component has finished the Process Validations phase.
      void startRenderResponse()
      Called when the component is about to begin rendering.

    • Method Detail

      • endProcessValidators

        void endProcessValidators()
        Called after the component has finished the Process Validations phase. If validations are processed but the Update Model Values phase is never reached, then validations probably failed.

      • endProcessUpdates

        void endProcessUpdates()
        Called after the component has finished the Update Model Values phase.

      • startRenderResponse

        void startRenderResponse()
        Called when the component is about to begin rendering.
